Write  a program to count no.of words in a string

#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
 
void main()
{
    char s[200];
    int count = 0, i;
    printf("Enter the string: ");
    scanf("%[^\n]s", s);
    for (i = 0;s[i] != '\0';i++)
    {
        if (s[i] == ' ')
            count++;    
    }
    printf("Number of words in given string are: %d\n", count + 1);
}

INPUT AND OUTPUT:

Enter the string: i love india
Number of words in given string are: 3
